---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Elite Host – Premium Web Hosting Services for Your Business"
  description="Elite Host offers top-tier, reliable, and fast web hosting services tailored to meet the unique needs of businesses. Our hosting solutions are designed for performance, security, and scalability, ensuring your website runs smoothly 24/7."
  keywords="Elite Host, premium web hosting, business web hosting, reliable hosting, fast web hosting, secure web hosting, scalable hosting solutions, high-performance hosting, hosting services for businesses, 24/7 website hosting"
  author="RedCheap"
  ogTitle="Elite Host – Premium Web Hosting Services for Your Business"
  ogDescription="Elite Host offers top-tier, reliable, and fast web hosting services tailored to meet the unique needs of businesses. Our hosting solutions are designed for performance, security, and scalability, ensuring your website runs smoothly 24/7."
  ogImage="URL_to_image"
  ogUrl="Your Website URL"
  twitterTitle="Elite Host – Premium Web Hosting Services for Your Business"
  twitterDescription="Elite Host offers top-tier, reliable, and fast web hosting services tailored to meet the unique needs of businesses. Our hosting solutions are designed for performance, security, and scalability, ensuring your website runs smoothly 24/7."
  twitterImage="URL_to_image"
>
  <!-- =====================
  Banner
  ===================== -->
  <div class="main-banner page-banner">
    <div class="img-up">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="inner-content"> <span class="top-heading">WordPress Hosting</span>
              <h1>High-performance hosting for WordPress websites.</h1>
              <h3>Optimized speed, security, and updates.</h3>
              <ul class="banner-list icon">
                <li><i class="bi bi-lightning-charge me-2"></i>Blazing Fast Performance</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-speedometer2 me-2"></i>User Friendly Control Panel</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-clock me-2"></i>99% Uptime Guarantee</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-headset me-2"></i>24/7 Expert Support</li>
              </ul>
              <h4 class="mt-3"> <span>Starts at just</span> <sup>৳</sup> <strong>259</strong> <small>/mo</small> </h4>
              <div class="inline-btns mt-3"> <a class="btns one" href="#plans">Get Started Now<i class="far fa-arrow-right"></i></a> </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="text-center text-lg-end"> <img src="/images/wordpress_banner.png" alt="Reseller Hosting"> </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- =======================
  Plan Section
  ====================== -->

  <section id="plans" class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-header center gap-bottom">
            <h2>Choose Your Plan</h2>
            <p>Get optimized speed, top-tier NVMe SSD storage, and enterprise-grade reliability tailored for Bangladeshi businesses.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="swiper swiper-plans">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
              <!-- Plan 1: WP Starter -->
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="plans-design-one"> <img src="/images/database.png" alt="icon" class="icon">
                  <h3>WP Starter</h3>
                  <p>Perfect for personal portfolios.</p>
                  <h6>৳259 / month</h6>
                  <h4> <sup>৳</sup> 2,490 <small>/year</small> <span class="badge-plan">Save 20%</span> </h4>
                  <a class="btns three" href="">Select Plan</a>
                  <ul>
                    <li><i class="ri-global-line"></i> 1 WordPress Website</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-hard-drive-2-line"></i> 5 GB NVMe SSD Storage</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-exchange-line"></i> 100 GB Bandwidth</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-dashboard-line"></i> 1 Core CPU / 1 GB RAM</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-globe"></i> LiteSpeed Web Server</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-lock"></i> Free SSL & Daily Backups</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Plan 2: WP Pro -->
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="plans-design-one"> <img src="/images/server.png" alt="icon" class="icon">
                  <h3>WP Pro</h3>
                  <p>Ideal for growing blogs & sites.</p>
                  <h6>৳389 / month</h6>
                  <h4> <sup>৳</sup> 3,690 <small>/year</small> <span class="badge-plan">Save 20%</span> </h4>
                  <a class="btns three" href="">Select Plan</a>
                  <ul>
                    <li><i class="ri-global-line"></i> 3 WordPress Websites</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-hard-drive-2-line"></i> 15 GB NVMe SSD Storage</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-exchange-line"></i> Unmetered Bandwidth</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-dashboard-line"></i> 2 Core CPU / 2 GB RAM</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-globe"></i> LiteSpeed Web Server</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-lock"></i> Free SSL & Daily Backups</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Plan 3: WP Business -->
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="plans-design-one"> <img src="/images/servers.png" alt="icon" class="icon">
                  <h3>WP Business</h3>
                  <p>Great for WooCommerce websites.</p>
                  <h6>৳499 / month</h6>
                  <h4> <sup>৳</sup> 4,790 <small>/year</small> <span class="badge-plan">Save 20%</span> </h4>
                  <a class="btns three" href="">Select Plan</a>
                  <ul>
                    <li><i class="ri-global-line"></i> 10 WordPress Websites</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-hard-drive-2-line"></i> 35 GB NVMe SSD Storage</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-exchange-line"></i> Unmetered Bandwidth</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-dashboard-line"></i> 3 Core CPU / 4 GB RAM</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-globe"></i> LiteSpeed Web Server</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-lock"></i> Free SSL & WAF Security</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Plan 4: WP Enterprise -->
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="plans-design-one"> <img src="/images/cloud.png" alt="icon" class="icon">
                  <h3>WP Enterprise</h3>
                  <p>Ultimate power for large sites.</p>
                  <h6>৳629 / month</h6>
                  <h4> <sup>৳</sup> 5,990 <small>/year</small> <span class="badge-plan">Save 20%</span> </h4>
                  <a class="btns three" href="">Select Plan</a>
                  <ul>
                    <li><i class="ri-global-line"></i> Unlimited Websites</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-hard-drive-2-line"></i> 75 GB NVMe SSD Storage</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-exchange-line"></i> Unmetered Bandwidth</li>
                    <li><i class="ri-dashboard-line"></i> 4 Core CPU / 6 GB RAM</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-globe"></i> LiteSpeed Web Server</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-lock"></i> Advanced Security Suite</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-header gap-bottom center">
            <h2>It just works Auto-magically</h2>
            <p>A secure, reliable and powerful platform crafted for WordPress</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-lg-5 gy-4 justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-one">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/resource.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Auto-Setup</h4>
              <p>No need for any legwork - Your WordPress hosting comes pre-configured with the latest version of WordPress and is ready-to-use the moment you buy it.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-one">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/data-processing.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Auto-Updates</h4>
              <p>Any patches or version upgrades released by WordPress are automatically installed for your packages, not only making your sites future-proof but also more secure.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-one">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/data-storage.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Auto-Caching</h4>
              <p>Get the best-performing WordPress sites with our Cloud Hosting. With cache and CDN auto-configured on all your packages, pages load much faster with the least amount of resources.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-one">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/data-transfer.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Auto-Backups</h4>
              <p>Get a time machine for all your WordPress sites. With CodeGuard automatically set up for any site you create, your data is always protected and regularly backed up.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-one">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/data-protection.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Auto-Secured</h4>
              <p>No need to worry about viruses or hacking attempts. All your WordPress sites will be regularly scanned for malware with SiteLock's advanced security tools.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-gap bg1">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-between">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="plan-description">
            <div>
              <h4>Create Hosting Website In Minutes</h4>
              <p>Effortlessly create your hosting website in minutes with our intuitive platform. No coding skills required. Launch your site quickly and efficiently with our user-friendly tools.</p>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                  <ul class="list-check list-flex">
                    <li>Assured Speed</li>
                    <li>Numerous Domains</li>
                    <li>Ideal Protection</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                  <ul class="list-check list-flex">
                    <li>24/7 Full Support</li>
                    <li>Advanced Storage</li>
                    <li>Secured Databases</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5">
          <div class="plan-description"> <img src="/images/website.png" alt="reseller"> </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-header gap-bottom center">
            <h2>Your WordPress Site - powered by our Cloud Hosting</h2>
            <p>Experience seamless performance and reliability with our Cloud Hosting powering your WordPress site today!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-lg-5 gy-4 justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="content">
              <h4><i class="bi bi-cpu"></i> &nbsp;Blazing-Fast Load Time</h4>
              <p>With top-of-the-line hardware and caching - which stores your site’s most used pages, and a globally distributed CDN, your site is served upto 2x faster.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="content">
              <h4><i class="bi bi-database"></i> &nbsp;Instant Scaling</h4>
              <p>No need to move your hosting as your traffic grows. Ramp up your resources at the click of a button - instantly add RAM and CPU without a reboot.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="content">
              <h4><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i> &nbsp;Your Data - Safeguarded</h4>
              <p>Our industry-leading Ceph-based storage system stores your website data across 3 distinct devices to ensure redundancy and safety.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="content">
              <h4><i class="bi bi-send"></i> &nbsp;Automatic Failover</h4>
              <p>If we detect a hardware issue, we automatically move your site to another server, ensuring that your site is always up and you never lose traffic.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="content">
              <h4><i class="bi bi-intersect"></i> &nbsp;One-Click Staging</h4>
              <p>Test updates, new plugins, and code modifications in a secure sandbox staging environment before deploying them live with a single click.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="content">
              <h4><i class="bi bi-shield-lock"></i> &nbsp;Advanced Security Suite</h4>
              <p>Sleep easy knowing your site is protected with automatic malware scans, a real-time web application firewall (WAF), and free SSL certificates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10 bg1 support">
          <div class="row g-4 align-items-center justify-content-between">
            <div class="col-lg-7">
              <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Not sure where to Start?</h2>
                <p>
                  Talk to one of our hosting specialist who will review your needs and propose a tailored hosting solution that will match your specific business reality and needs.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-3">
                  <ul>
                    <li class="text-center">
                      <span class="icon"><img src="/images/talk.webp" alt="" /></span>
                      <label class="content">+8801712345678</label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-center">
                      <span class="icon"><img src="/images/support2.webp" alt="" /></span>
                      <label class="content">24/7/365 Support</label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-center">
                      <span class="icon"><img src="/images/customer.webp" alt="" /></span>
                      <label class="content">Instant Live Chat</label>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
              <div class="text-center text-lg-end">
                <img src="/images/support-center.png" alt="Technical Support" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <div class="section-header gap-bottom center">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Get the answers to frequently asked questions about our premium hosting service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10">
          <ul class="accordion">
            <li>
              <h5>Can I upgrade my WordPress Hosting plan?</h5>
              <p>Yes, absolutely! You can scale your CPU and RAM resources instantly with a single click from your dashboard as your website traffic grows. If you need to upgrade to a higher tier plan for more SSD storage or additional features, our dedicated support team is available 24/7/365 to handle the transition for you seamlessly.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Can I add more WordPress installations to an existing plan?</h5>
              <p>Our WordPress hosting plans are designed with dedicated resources per installation to guarantee peak performance and security. The number of allowed WordPress sites is fixed per plan tier, but you can easily purchase a larger plan or add a separate subscription if you need to host additional websites.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Can SiteLock and CodeGuard packages be upgraded?</h5>
              <p>Yes! While our plans include robust default scanning and backup features, you can easily upgrade to higher tiers of SiteLock (for advanced database scanning and vulnerability patching) or CodeGuard (for increased cloud storage capacity and on-demand backups) at any time.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Can I use an external email service with WordPress Hosting?</h5>
              <p>Yes, you are completely free to use any third-party email provider (such as Google Workspace, Microsoft 365, or Zoho Mail) with your domain. Simply update your domain's custom MX and DNS records in your dashboard, or reach out to our team for fast assistance.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Can I use an existing SSL certificate with my blog?</h5>
              <p>Yes! While every hosting plan comes with a free, pre-configured SSL certificate from Let's Encrypt, you can easily import and install your own custom or pre-existing third-party SSL certificates directly through the dashboard.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Will WordPress be updated automatically?</h5>
              <p>Yes! We enable automatic WordPress core updates by default to ensure your website always has the latest features, security patches, and performance optimizations. We also perform a quick automated backup before major upgrades so you can restore your site instantly if any plugin conflicts arise.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Is there a money-back period for WordPress Hosting?</h5>
              <p>Yes, we offer a comprehensive 30-day money-back guarantee on our premium WordPress Hosting packages. If you are not fully satisfied with our speed, performance, or support within your first 30 days, we will issue a full refund—no questions asked.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Is Multisite supported with WordPress Hosting?</h5>
              <p>Yes! WordPress Multisite is fully supported on our larger hosting plans. If you plan to deploy a network of blogs or sub-sites, our high-performance cloud architecture and automated scaling features will ensure your network runs fast and reliably.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Can I access the cPanel for my hosting plan?</h5>
              <p>No, our WordPress Hosting uses a custom, hyper-focused WordPress Management Dashboard instead of traditional, cluttered cPanel. This tailored dashboard is engineered to give you effortless, lightning-fast control over backups, staging environments, PHP configurations, and WordPress-specific settings.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Is an SSL Certificate included with the plan?</h5>
              <p>Yes, a premium Let's Encrypt SSL certificate is pre-configured and completely free of charge for every domain associated with your hosting plan. It is automatically provisioned and renewed, securing your visitors' data and boosting your search engine ranking out of the box.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
